sentences: Ole Hamre (born 20 October 1959) is a Norwegian drummer.
Hamre is known for his collaboration with accordionist Gabriel Fliflet, including the duo Fliflet/Hamre (1991–) and the music group Fri Fri Flyt (1993–2001).
